'Merged PR 10322: Merged PR 10316: [Thermal] Thermal Ramp test method exception bug fix.'
'Merged PR 9910: Fixed UEI start call for TOS3'
'Merged PR 9804: Updating Thermal related documentation'
'Merged PR 9455: [ThermalService] Updating TCC library for TOS321'
'Merged PR 9292: PCS token for CHECK_DIE_FORCE standardized to other PCS ituff prints'</releaseNotes>
